---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import GetInTouchBanner from "../../components/common/GetInTouchBanner.tsx";
---

<BaseLayout title="Industry-University-Research Cooperation Agreement - BBSD">
  <main>
    <article class="bg-white py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-light">Apr 18, 2025</p>
        <h1 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-dark md:text-5xl">
          Our Company Signs Industry-University-Research Strategic Cooperation
          Agreement with Nantong University
        </h1>

        <img
          src="/images/news/signing.jpg"
          alt="Signing Ceremony"
          class="mb-10 w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
        />

        <div
          class="prose max-w-none space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray"
        >
          <p>
            On the morning of April 18, our company signed an
            Industry-University-Research Strategic Cooperation Agreement with
            Nantong University. Hua Liang, Member of the Standing Committee of
            the Party Committee and Vice President of Nantong University, and
            Shi Haowen, Vice President of BBSD Holding B.V., attended the event.
          </p>

          <p>
            On behalf of Nantong University, Hua Liang extended a warm welcome
            to Shi Haowen and his delegation, and introduced the university's
            development history, school-running philosophy, school-running
            characteristics and achievements made in recent years. He stated
            that Nantong University has always regarded serving the local
            economic and social development as an important mission, actively
            providing talent and intellectual support as well as scientific and
            technological innovation support for local development.
          </p>

          <p>
            He expressed the expectation that both the university and the
            enterprise will further deepen cooperation, continuously expand the
            scope of cooperation, and work together to create a sound situation
            of win-win cooperation.
          </p>

          <p>
            Shi Haowen introduced the company's situation, noting that as a
            wholly owned subsidiary of Jord Oil & Gas Systems B.V., a Dutch
            marine engineering equipment enterprise, the company has developed
            into a world-leading provider of design, procurement and
            construction services for floating production, storage and
            offloading (FPSO) topside modules, with customers in nearly 100
            countries around the world.
          </p>

          <p>
            He expressed the expectation that both parties will focus on the
            fields of marine equipment manufacturing and new energy and carry
            out comprehensive industry-university-research cooperation in terms
            of talent exchange and interaction, joint research projects,
            transformation of scientific and technological achievements, and
            co-construction of innovation platforms.
          </p>

          <p>
            At the meeting, Xu Yiming, Dean of the School of Electrical
            Engineering and Automation, and Lu Liangjun, General Manager of our
            company, signed the Industry-University-Research Strategic
            Cooperation Agreement on behalf of both the university and the
            enterprise. Jorik Bik, Vice President, introduced the company's FPSO
            projects in the United Kingdom, the United Arab Emirates and other
            countries. Dr. Li Zhen from the School of Electrical Engineering and
            Automation presented the achievements of Nantong University in the
            fields of ship and marine engineering, new energy, etc.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a
            href="/news"
            class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-link hover:underline"
            >← Back to News</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <GetInTouchBanner client:visible />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
